data.description: Welcome to the country life!   This well maintained 3-bedroom, 2 bathroom home sits on 10.07 acres (Approx 438,649 sf) of land!   Home features a split floor plan with two living areas; one with a cozy woodstove.   The kitchen is updated and boasts porcelain countertops, an abundance of cabinet space, and plenty of room to work.   Master suite is generous in size with dual vanities, a relaxing garden tub and dual closets.   Outside are multiple storage sheds and 2 Connex containers for extra storage.  With 2 corrals for your furry family members, this home checks all the boxes.
